{"tid":2188860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"法國記者Valentin Gendrot 卧底入警隊2年 離職後出書揭法國警暴問題","createTime":"2020-09-04T13:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T21:00:49.000Z","uid":222970,"like":494,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb9d90eb32931e039d1db82a90f2d979ba716bf","tid":2188860,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H7C0bBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH7C0bBw.png&h=ccbdf72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國記者Valentin Gendrot 卧底入警隊2年 離職後出書揭法國警暴問題<br />\n<br />\n一名法國記者為了解警隊文化，親身加入法國警隊，之後更將經歷輯錄成書。他形容警隊有嚴重的種族歧視及暴力文化，而且警員經常有著報復心態。<br />\n<br />\n該名法國記者叫 Valentin Gendrot ，他在巴黎北部的一間警局中任職了約六個月。在此之前他先在警察學校受訓三個月，之後被分配到警察精神科小隊，工作15個月後被調派往前線警局，並獲給予制服及配槍，可以外出巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n他形容警隊暴力行為成為常態，又指自己曾經被迫偽造證據，指控一名被警員毆打的少年。Gendrot 指出.............................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0af1FvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0af1FvR.jpg&h=04989780&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YKB8kvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYKB8kvR.jpg&h=75eb9c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>全文請入link睇</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dbchannel.hk/2020/09/04/法國記者valentin-gendrot-卧底入警隊2年-離職後出書揭法國警暴/?fbclid=IwAR1IZ3ljcWD8skzPkvmHyLIlywQMqeJEA1SGCdquo1Np9piFKablepX9vPg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbchannel.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F04%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85valentin-gendrot-%E5%8D%A7%E5%BA%95%E5%85%A5%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A2%E5%B9%B4-%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E5%BE%8C%E5%87%BA%E6%9B%B8%E6%8F%AD%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%A6%E6%9A%B4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1IZ3ljcWD8skzPkvmHyLIlywQMqeJEA1SGCdquo1Np9piFKablepX9vPg&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cfZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=f6b47d5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dbchannel.hk/20